368c4483585efd1a48344ea3a367473e2b8","tid":1420800,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4e97fa9733e90be94a8277107c96b47c58db4c9d","tid":1420800,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9cb73c2bafa0a262fd97ba03e8bc704000b6fa79","tid":1420800,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"591f0e56ff9bbc2d3d54a4136383bad6dd87043a","tid":1420800,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"511d85c60904ba052f7b75c51103161bf0a41060","tid":1420800,"uid":193972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"放心, 我一定唔割 唔篤灰 <br />\n亦都係今次咁多人賭上生命前途咁出嚟<br />\n我覺得我有責任去一齊爭取, 唔應該將責任同負擔由年輕人揹起晒<br />\n我唔係次次出到嚟, 但出到嘅都出<br />\n亦盡量去解釋同影響身邊嘅人去理解而家發生嘅事<br />\n<br />\n有人同我講, 話阻人返工唔啱, 阻路唔啱<br />\n屌鳩我話我支持運動, 叫我解釋點解要咁做<br />\n我同佢哋講：咁你有咩建議係切實可行又會令到政府正面回應?<br />\n我唔會話佢哋唔啱, 因為大家都摸索緊可以點樣令到政府回應<br />\n如果我冇提議俾到大家, 我更唔會有資格可以指責<br />\n<br />\n香港人係一個令我自豪嘅身份<br />\n因為有一群熱愛香港而且出心出力去守護香港嘅人喺度<br />\n係大家對香港嘅珍惜令我自豪<br />\n而我亦會繼續珍惜香港, 守護香港"},{"pid":"ccdb3d40caabc472a6e59215446dc2c632ec22f4","tid":1420800,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4f6f7434e52502482e62603dd971c26a3222c5","tid":1420800,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲嘅回覆真係令我心頭一暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddc23737454ae1fa8bb0bfffda12deef4ce65a3","tid":1420800,"uid":265901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"小朋友多謝你 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e9ac8f2d67c1f960bbdd5675024e508058e